Excel Signature will, on Sunday, present Jude Olotu’s solo exhibition, titled: Moods Relic of Courage. The exhibition, which holds at Thought Pyramid Art Centre, Abuja, will run till April 18. Olotu has participated in international shows, such as  World Art Dubai exhibition, New York and France, showcasing his style of eclectic art. He has featured in group and individual exhibitions in Nigeria.   ‘Restriction of homeowners unlawful’     Aspirant: pray against insecurity     2023: APC declares nomination forms free for women aspirants   His works stood out among the best in a plethora of exhibited art works at the World Art Dubai exhibition. Olotu has created and nurtured many talents and students of arts, which has led to the creation of Excel Signature Creative Hub in Abuja. The creative hub is a place where creative artists are nurtured in fine arts, digital arts, metal art, wood art, sculpturing, product design, cinematography and production, music, and photography. Olotu hails from Niger Delta. His love for art started as a child growing up in Jos.